nodes.text: In 27 BBY, a male Whiphid visited the Coruscant cantina known as the Twirling Twi'lek. The Whiphid attacked and was killed by the notorious bounty hunter Jango Fett.
This individual was created for Star Wars: Jango Fett, published by Dark Horse Comics in 2002. The comic issue was written by Ron Marz and illustrated by Tom Fowler.
